attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Nestled in one of the most coveted and historical areas of South Boston, this 3 unit investment property is just steps away from breathtaking views atop the Heights and within walking distance of the trendiest bars and restaurants in the neighborhood. The first-floor unit offers 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and features two expansive private decks, each over 150 square feet. Unit 2 includes a spacious 1-bedroom layout with an alcove, perfect for a home office, and a private 150+ square foot deck that showcases stunning city and water views of points south. With an open layout, hardwood floors throughout, and generously sized rooms, this unit maximizes both comfort and style. Unit 3 mirrors this appeal with its large bedroom, 1.0 bathroom, and a dedicated workspace, all accompanied by picturesque views.
